name: Ket Maliss, Shadow Killer
Lore: 'Assassins are highly valued by Jabba the Hutt and other gangsters. Ket Maliss, Prince Xizor''s ''shadow killer,'' has unknown but undoubtedly lethal business in Mos Eisley. Assassin.',
Text: 'Adds two to the power of anything he pilots. While with opponent''s character of ability > 2, Ket Maliss is power +1 and defense value + 2 and draws one battle destiny if unable to otherwise. Whenever opponent''s character was lost from same site, opponent loses 1 Force.',
